<plot>'Mask in the Mirror' is a New York tale of two women, each hiding her own demons behind a mask of quiet desperation. As their lives become more entangled, their masks begin to slip and those demons are released. Laura Bluemount, model with an attitude, a drinking problem, a sex problem, a mother problem and a money problem. She needs a roommate. Enter Linda Benson, a quiet older woman who appears untroubled and is willing to pay the rent. Soon Laura discovers clues about Linda that lead her to believe that there's trouble ahead.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?360123</url></doc>
